James Watt kɛ ɛjaɖɛ nɖɩ payaɣ-ɖɩ size [[Ekɔsɩ]] yɔ, ɖɩ-ɛjaɖɛ  taa tʋ. Ɛkɛ abalʋ sɔsɔ nɔɔyʋ Ekɔsɩ ɛjaɖɛ taa peeɖe. Palʋla-ɩ [[kɔlaɣ fenaɣ]] taa evemiye hiu (19) nɛ nakʋ n̄ɩŋgʋ wiye. Egeetiye  nɖɩ ɖɩ-tɛtʋ taa palʋla-ɩ yɔɔ payaɣ size Greenock tɛtʋ Ekɔsɩ ɛjaɖɛ taa.
[[Fichier:James_Watt_Memorial_College.jpg|vignette|James Watt Memorial College]]
[[Fichier:James_Watt's_Workshop.jpg|vignette|James Watt's Workshop]]Ɛsɩba [[kɩyɛɛna fenaɣ]] taa evemiye nɛɛlɛ nɛ kagbanzɩ (25) n̄ɩŋgʋ wiye pɩnaɣ 1819 n̄ɩŋga taa. 
Palʊla James Watt kɛ kɔlaɣ fenaɣ  kɩyakʊ  19 wiye pɩnaɣ 1736 kɛ Griŋnɔkɩ tɛtʊ taa, Ekɔsɩ ɛjaɖɛ taa nɛ ɛsɩ kɩyɛna fenaɣ 25 pɩnaɣ 1819 ɛwɛna pɩnzɩ 83 Aŋgletɛɛrɩ ɛjaɖɛ taa. Ɛkɛna tomnasɩ lɛɣzɩtʊ ñɩnɩyʊ, kpɛlɩ kpɛlɩ pɩsɩʊ kpɛlɛkɩyʊ nɛ ŋgbɛyɛ ñʊʊtʊ nɔɔyʊ. 

James ɖoo kɛ payaɣ se Agnes Muirhead nɛ ɛ-halaa kɔyɔ Ann  MaGregor  nɛ Peggy Miller nɛ e-piya kɔyɔ Margeret Watt nɛ Gregory Watt. Ɛnʊ kaawɛna ŋgbɛyɛ nɖɩ payaɣ-ɖɩ se Lunar Society nɛ ɖɩwɛ Pirmigam yɔ. Ɛzima ɛlaba tʊma sɔsɔna kɛ kpɛlɩ kpɛlɩ ñɩnɩʊ yɔɔ yɔ, nɛ pɩsa nɛ ɛ-hɩɖɛ ɖɛɛna ɛsɩnda ɖɔɖɔ yɔ kɛ pakpaɣa ɛ-hɩɖɛ se ɖɩkɛ keteŋga kpeekpe ɖoŋ ñɩnɩʊ kɩmaɣzʊ nɛ payaɣ-kʊ se Watt.
